# UI to Engine Access

- Import engine APIs only through `src/engine/public.ts` (or alias equivalent).
- Avoid deep imports into `src/engine/**` internals.
- UI should dispatch commands rather than mutating engine internals.
- Keep per-frame simulation/entity data out of Zustand stores.
- Keep debug toggles and tooling state in UI state, not domain state duplication.
